    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas of treeless, rolling terrain found in polar or alpine regions, typically covered with bare ground, rock, or such vegetation as mosses, lichens, and small shrubs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
